projects.name: Ecoverse Residence
projects.description:
Welcome to Ecoverse Residences, a prestigious real estate project set in the heart of Bali, where modern design meets eco-conscious living. Created by the visionary Nuanu Property Group in collaboration with OXO Living, this exclusive development offers an unparalleled living experience tailored for those who value sustainability, comfort, and privacy.

Highlights of Ecoverse Residences
Prime Location
Nestled amidst lush tropical greenery and serene rice fields, Ecoverse Residences provide a tranquil retreat from the bustle of urban life. Conveniently located near Bali's top attractions, it offers the perfect balance between seclusion and accessibility.

Exclusive Residences
With only 50 premium private units, including elegantly designed apartments and townhouses, Ecoverse promises exclusivity and sophistication. Each residence features:

Panoramic windows with breathtaking views of the surrounding nature.
High ceilings and open-plan layouts for an airy, spacious feel.
Luxurious finishes using natural materials like fine woods, marble, and glass.
Private terraces and lush gardens for select units.
Optional private pools for ultimate indulgence.
Unmatched Amenities
Ecoverse offers world-class facilities designed to complement a modern lifestyle:

25-meter infinity pool surrounded by tropical landscaping.
State-of-the-art gym and fitness center.
Stylish clubhouse, lounge, and co-working spaces.
Gourmet fine dining restaurant for a culinary delight.
Underground parking, 24/7 reception, and round-the-clock security.
Sustainability at Its Core
Ecoverse Residences redefine eco-luxury by incorporating innovative green technologies:

Solar panels and advanced insulation materials reduce energy consumption by up to 20%.
Rainwater harvesting for garden irrigation and efficient water usage.
Triple water purification system for clean, safe water.
Comprehensive waste recycling programs to reduce environmental impact.
Active, Healthy Living
Designed for those who appreciate balance, Ecoverse seamlessly integrates nature, culture, and wellness. Residents can enjoy thoughtfully crafted spaces for work, leisure, solitude, and sports.

Investment Opportunity
Scheduled for completion in 2025, Ecoverse Residences promise exceptional value appreciation in Bali's thriving real estate market. Whether you're looking for a luxurious home, a vacation property, or a profitable investment, Ecoverse delivers on all fronts.

Discover a lifestyle where luxury meets sustainability. Your dream eco-luxury residence awaits at Ecoverse.
